# Feature Organization Best Practices (meApp iOS)

## 1. Feature Structure
```
Features/{Feature}/
├── Views/
│   ├── Screens/           # Main screen views
│   └── Components/        # Reusable components
├── Stores/                # ViewModels/State management
├── Models/                # Feature-specific models
├── Strings/               # Localized strings
├── Routes/                # Navigation routes
├── Forms/                 # Form configurations
└── Enums/                 # Feature-specific enums
```

## 2. View Organization
- Separate screens and components.
- Use descriptive file names.
- Group related views in subdirectories.
- Maintain clear navigation flow.

---

**Summary:**
- All features must be organized for clarity, modularity, and scalability.
